    <item>
      <title>欧盟拟出台新拍卖规则 欲阻止中国氢能技术</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/eu-aims-to-block-chinese-hydrogen-tech-in-new-auction-guidelines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将采取措施，将中国制造的氢电解器排除在即将举行的拍卖之外，该拍卖旨在促进欧盟绿色转型期间的氢燃料生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/eu-aims-to-block-chinese-hydrogen-tech-in-new-auction-guidelines</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 11:15:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CD&R 将债务融资股权期权排除在赛诺菲最终竞标之外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/cd-r-excludes-debt-funded-equity-option-from-final-sanofi-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Clayton Dubilier &amp; Rice 提出的条件是，银行必须承担超过 10 亿欧元（11 亿美元）的债务，为竞购赛诺菲消费者健康部门提供部分股权检查资金，但这笔贷款并未出现在最终提交给这家制药公司的方案中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/cd-r-excludes-debt-funded-equity-option-from-final-sanofi-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:13:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>10 月降息预期升温，欧洲债券市场上涨势头增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/european-bonds-surge-with-ecb-cut-in-october-increasingly-likely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，欧元区政府债券的涨势加快，因又一批疲软的经济数据增强了该地区放松货币政策的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/european-bonds-surge-with-ecb-cut-in-october-increasingly-likely</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 08:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币摆脱季节性不利因素，9 月份涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/bitcoin-btc-heads-to-one-of-best-septembers-on-record-on-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以美联储为首的全球降息浪潮的帮助下，比特币这一最大的数字资产摆脱了季节性衰退，有望实现 9 月份最大涨幅之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/bitcoin-btc-heads-to-one-of-best-septembers-on-record-on-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 04:45:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
